---
const contactHref = 'mailto:hola@apprunners.app?subject=Quiero%20probar%20AppRunners';
const appPreviewStats = [
  ['12', 'apuntados'],
  ['7:30', 'domingo'],
  ['8 km', 'ritmo suave'],
];
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="AppRunners ayuda a grupos reales de runners a organizar quedadas, confirmar asistencia e invitar a gente nueva sin perderse en chats."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
    <title>AppRunners | Quedadas de running sin ruido</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero__content">
          <p class="eyebrow">Para grupos reales de runners</p>
          <h1>AppRunners</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Organiza quedadas, confirma quién viene e invita a nuevos corredores sin convertir cada salida en un hilo infinito.
          </p>
          <div class="actions" aria-label="Acciones principales">
            <a class="button button--primary" href={contactHref}>Pedir acceso</a>
            <a class="button button--secondary" href="#como-funciona">Ver cómo funciona</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phone" aria-label="Vista previa de una quedada en AppRunners">
          <div class="phone__status">
            <span>AppRunners</span>
            <span>Dom</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meetup">
            <p class="meetup__label">Próxima quedada</p>
            <h2>Salida por el río</h2>
            <p>Domingo · 7:30 · Parque Grande</p>
            <div class="stats">
              {appPreviewStats.map(([value, label]) => (
                <div class="stat">
                  <strong>{value}</strong>
                  <span>{label}</span>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
            <div class="runners" aria-label="Corredores apuntados">
              <span>AN</span>
              <span>MR</span>
              <span>LC</span>
              <span>+9</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="como-funciona" class="section">
        <div class="section__header">
          <p class="eyebrow">Menos fricción que WhatsApp</p>
          <h2>Lo necesario para que el grupo salga a correr</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="features">
          <article>
            <span class="icon">01</span>
            <h3>Crea la quedada</h3>
            <p>Distancia, punto de salida, hora y ritmo en una vista clara que cualquiera puede revisar.</p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <span class="icon">02</span>
            <h3>Confirma asistencia</h3>
            <p>El grupo ve al instante quién viene, sin contar mensajes ni reacciones dispersas.</p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <span class="icon">03</span>
            <h3>Invita fácil</h3>
            <p>Un código permite meter a alguien nuevo en el grupo antes de la próxima salida.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cta">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Primeros grupos</p>
          <h2>Estamos abriendo acceso a grupos pequeños.</h2>
        </div>
        <a class="button button--primary" href={contactHref}>Quiero probarlo</a>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    color-scheme: light;
    font-family:
      Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
      sans-serif;
    background: #f7f3ec;
    color: #17201b;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    min-width: 320px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 44%),
      #f7f3ec;
  }

  a {
    color: inherit;
  }

  main {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(300px, 420px);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 88vh;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    padding-bottom: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(23, 32, 27, 0.12);
  }

  .hero__content {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    color: #236a53;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1,
  h2,
  h3,
  p {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: clamp(3.6rem, 12vw, 9rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .lead {
    max-width: 660px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #334139;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.2vw, 1.7rem);
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-flex;
    min-height: 48px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      transform 160ms ease,
      box-shadow 160ms ease,
      background-color 160ms ease;
  }

  .button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .button--primary {
    background: #17201b;
    color: #fffdfa;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(23, 32, 27, 0.18);
  }

  .button--secondary {
    border: 1px solid rgba(23, 32, 27, 0.2);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52);
    color: #17201b;
  }

  .phone {
    width: min(100%, 390px);
    margin-inline: auto;
    border: 10px solid #17201b;
    border-radius: 36px;
    background: #fffdfa;
    box-shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(23, 32, 27, 0.22);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .phone__status {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
    color: #64716a;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .meetup {
    margin: 0 1rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.15rem;
    background: #eaf5ef;
  }

  .meetup__label {
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    color: #236a53;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .meetup h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .meetup p:not(.meetup__label) {
    color: #4b5d52;
  }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0.55rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .stat {
    min-width: 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: #fffdfa;
  }

  .stat strong,
  .stat span {
    display: block;
  }

  .stat strong {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .stat span {
    color: #64716a;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .runners {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.45rem;
  }

  .runners span {
    display: inline-grid;
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #17201b;
    color: #fffdfa;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .section {
    padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem) clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
  }

  .section__header {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .section h2,
  .cta h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .features article {
    min-height: 220px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(23, 32, 27, 0.12);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: #fffdfa;
  }

  .icon {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    color: #236a53;
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .features h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  .features p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: #4b5d52;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    background: #dcece4;
  }

  .cta > div {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .phone {
      max-width: 360px;
    }

    .features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta {
      display: block;
    }

    .cta .button {
      margin-top: 1.4rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .hero {
      padding-inline: 1.25rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3.1rem, 18vw, 4.8rem);
    }

    .actions,
    .button {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
